362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Photo by Kevin Voigt/GettyImages) Bishop Barron suggested the left is being open about how they are opponents of Christianity, saying, \\\"I think, folks, what's interesting here is this deeply secularist, postmodern society knows who its enemy is.\", \"from\": 3392, \"to\": 3639, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3428, \"end\": 3434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\", \"score\": 0.9970056667405719, \"rank\": 0.0030033262189050696, \"text\": \"Bishop\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\"}, {\"begin\": 3435, \"end\": 3441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999983438101, \"rank\": 1.6559271249813905e-09, \"text\": \"Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 3507, \"end\": 3519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9387456045776706, \"rank\": 0.06525132441149563, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(Photo\", \"from\": 3392, \"to\": 3398}, {\"ngram\": \"Kevin Voigt/GettyImages\", \"from\": 3402, \"to\": 3425}, {\"ngram\": \"the left\", \"from\": 3451, \"to\": 3459}, {\"ngram\": \"opponents\", \"from\": 3493, \"to\": 3502}, {\"ngram\": \"folks\", \"from\": 3538, \"to\": 3543}, {\"ngram\": \"postmodern society\", \"from\": 3596, \"to\": 3614}, {\"ngram\": \"its enemy\", \"from\": 3625, \"to\": 3634}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are naming it.\", \"from\": 3640, \"to\": 3659, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And we should believe them.\\\"\", \"from\": 3660, \"to\": 3688, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He then urged Catholics and Christians not to cower or stay meek in the face of such anti-Christian bigotry, adding, \\\"We Christians, we Catholics should not be sheepish, we should resist, we should make our voices heard.\\\"\", \"from\": 3690, \"to\": 3911, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3704, \"end\": 3713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.998881951132125e-17, \"text\": \"Catholics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 3718, \"end\": 3728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.6264850349081303, \"rank\": 0.5935969929344702, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 3775, \"end\": 3789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antichrist\", \"score\": 0.9999999999281499, \"rank\": 5.2438174044309436e-11, \"text\": \"anti-Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antichrist\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antichrist\"}, {\"begin\": 3811, \"end\": 3821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.6264850349081303, \"rank\": 0.5935969929344702, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 3826, \"end\": 3835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.998881951132125e-17, \"text\": \"Catholics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"meek\", \"from\": 3750, \"to\": 3754}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 3758, \"to\": 3766}, {\"ngram\": \"our voices\", \"from\": 3893, \"to\": 3903}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement to Fox News Digital, Barron instructed Christians on how they can push back on this antagonism, stating, \\\"Christians should always resist evil, and I think we have indeed become too weak in the face of our cultural antagonists.\", \"from\": 3913, \"to\": 4155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3931, \"end\": 3939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.527873647828819e-19, \"text\": \"Fox News\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\"}, {\"begin\": 3949, \"end\": 3955, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999983438101, \"rank\": 1.6559271249813905e-09, \"text\": \"Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 3967, \"end\": 3977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.6264850349081303, \"rank\": 0.5935969929344702, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 4034, \"end\": 4044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.6264850349081303, \"rank\": 0.5935969929344702, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 3916, \"to\": 3927}, {\"ngram\": \"this antagonism\", \"from\": 4007, \"to\": 4022}, {\"ngram\": \"evil\", \"from\": 4066, \"to\": 4070}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 4118, \"to\": 4126}, {\"ngram\": \"our cultural antagonists\", \"from\": 4130, \"to\": 4154}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jesus' command to turn the other cheek is by no means equivalent to passivity, as is evident in the work ofMartin Luther King.\\\"\", \"from\": 4156, \"to\": 4283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4156, \"end\": 4161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999986639523, \"rank\": 1.3362108194503513e-09, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}, {\"begin\": 4270, \"end\": 4276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Luther\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5595328850342274e-47, \"text\": \"Luther\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Luther\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Luther\"}, {\"begin\": 4277, \"end\": 4281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King\", \"score\": 0.9510184498490267, \"rank\": 0.05133295074291526, \"text\": \"King\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the other cheek\", \"from\": 4179, \"to\": 4194}, {\"ngram\": \"no means\", \"from\": 4201, \"to\": 4209}, {\"ngram\": \"passivity\", \"from\": 4224, \"to\": 4233}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 4252, \"to\": 4260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"King used non-violent means to interrupt forms of wickedness that had embedded themselves into our society.\", \"from\": 4285, \"to\": 4393, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"King\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4290}, {\"ngram\": \"non-violent means\", \"from\": 4296, \"to\": 4313}, {\"ngram\": \"interrupt forms\", \"from\": 4317, \"to\": 4332}, {\"ngram\": \"wickedness\", \"from\": 4336, \"to\": 4346}, {\"ngram\": \"our society\", \"from\": 4381, \"to\": 4392}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Turning the other cheek and going the extra mile are practical strategies for mirroring a person's injustice back to him so that he might stop what he is doing and repent,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 4394, \"to\": 4575, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the other cheek\", \"from\": 4402, \"to\": 4417}, {\"ngram\": \"the extra mile\", \"from\": 4428, \"to\": 4442}, {\"ngram\": \"practical strategies\", \"from\": 4447, \"to\": 4467}, {\"ngram\": \"a person's injustice\", \"from\": 4482, \"to\": 4502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Barron continued, noting, \\\"We should follow the example of King in his battle for justice: call evil out, name it for what it is, make its negativity known, and endeavor to get in its way.\\\"\", \"from\": 4577, \"to\": 4767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4577, \"end\": 4583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999983438101, \"rank\": 1.6559271249813905e-09, \"text\": \"Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the example\", \"from\": 4621, \"to\": 4632}, {\"ngram\": \"King\", \"from\": 4636, \"to\": 4640}, {\"ngram\": \"his battle\", \"from\": 4644, \"to\": 4654}, {\"ngram\": \"justice\", \"from\": 4659, \"to\": 4666}, {\"ngram\": \"evil\", \"from\": 4673, \"to\": 4677}, {\"ngram\": \"its negativity\", \"from\": 4712, \"to\": 4726}, {\"ngram\": \"its way\", \"from\": 4757, \"to\": 4764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also stressed how effective social media can be in fighting evil, saying, \\\"I do believe that today the social media give us a means to accomplish all of these ends.\", \"from\": 4768, \"to\": 4935, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"how effective social media\", \"from\": 4785, \"to\": 4811}, {\"ngram\": \"evil\", \"from\": 4831, \"to\": 4835}, {\"ngram\": \"the social media\", \"from\": 4870, \"to\": 4886}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4892, \"to\": 4894}, {\"ngram\": \"a means\", \"from\": 4895, \"to\": 4902}, {\"ngram\": \"these ends\", \"from\": 4924, \"to\": 4934}]},